==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: man-made
<hw>man-made</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>Not of natural origin; prepared
or made by humans; artificial; of substances, made by chemical reaction
rather than extracted from a natural source; <as>as, <ex>man-made</ex>
fibers; <ex>man-made</ex> gems</as>. Opposed to
<ant>natural</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> semisynthetic, synthetic.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>man-made fiber</ent>⟦br⟧
